dct_description_sm: From Netherlands Government surveys between 1907 and 1914.
Depths shown by soundings and tints; relief by spot heights and form lines.
Buoy legend, tidal information chart, latitudinal and longitudinal lines.
Shows reefs, low water, buildings, waterways, railroads.
Authorities include Netherlands chart 135, Admiralty chart 2779, and H.O. charts 3121, 3123.
